ailable in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meta\"><code>&lt;meta&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meter\"><code>&lt;meter&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>N\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"nonStdElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nobr\"><code>&lt;nobr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement deprecatedElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/noframes\"><code>&lt;noframes&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/noscript\"><code>&lt;noscript&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>O\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object\"><code>&lt;object&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ol\"><code>&lt;ol&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/optgroup\"><code>&lt;optgroup&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/option\"><code>&lt;option&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/output\"><code>&lt;output&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>P\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/p\"><code>&lt;p&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/param\"><code>&lt;param&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/picture\"><code>&lt;picture&gt;</code></a></li>