le=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Shadow\"><code>&lt;shadow&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/slot\"><code>&lt;slot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/small\"><code>&lt;small&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/source\"><code>&lt;source&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"nonStdElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/spacer\"><code>&lt;spacer&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement deprecatedElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strike\"><code>&lt;strike&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard obsolete\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Veraltet:</strong> Dieses Feature ist veraltet. Obwohl es in manchen Browsern immer noch funktioniert, wird von seiner Benutzung abgeraten, da es jederzeit entfernt werden kann. Es sollte daher nicht mehr verwendet werden.</p></div></div>\n\n<p>Mit dem HTML Acronym Element (<code>&lt;acronym&gt;</code>) können Autoren eine Folge von Zeichen deutlich angeben, aus denen ein Akronym oder eine Abkürzung für ein Wort besteht. Dieses Element wurde in HTML5 entfernt. Verwenden Sie das Element <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/abbr\"><code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code></a>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\">\n<p><strong>Nutzungshinweis:</strong> Dieses Element wurde in HTML5 entfernt und sollte nicht mehr verwendet werden. Stattdessen sollten Webentwickler das Element <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/abbr\"><code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code></a> verwenden.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attributes","title":"Attribute","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dieses Element hat nur <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">globale Attribute (en-US)</a>, die allen Elementen gemeinsam sind.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"dom_interface","title":"DOM Schnittstelle","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dieses Element implementiert die <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Schnittstelle.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect4\"><strong>Implementierungshinweis: </strong>Bis einschließlich Gecko 1.9.2 implementiert Firefox die <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSpanElement\"><code>HTMLSpanElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Schnittstelle für dieses Element.</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Das <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>acronym</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>World Wide Web<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>WWW<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>acronym</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> ist nur eine Komponente des Internets.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"default_styling","title":"Standarddarstellung","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Obwohl der Zweck dieses Tags nur der Bequemlichkeit des Autors dient, variiert sein Standardstil von Browser zu Browser:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>Manche Browser, wie der Internet Explorer, stellen es nicht anders als das <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>-Element dar.</li>\n <li>Opera, Firefox, Chrome und einige andere fügen dem Inhalt des Elements eine gepunktete Unterstreichung hinzu.</li>\n <li>Einige Browser fügen nicht nur eine gepunktete Unterstreichung hinzu, sondern setzen sie auch in Kapitälchen ein. Um dies zu vermeiden, fügen Sie Ihrem CSS etwas wie <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/font-variant\"><code>font-variant</code></a><code>: none</code> hinzu.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Es wird daher dringend empfohlen, dass sich Webautoren nicht vollständig auf das Standard-Styling verlassen.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html401/struct/text.html#edef-ACRONYM\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 4.01 Specification<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von '&lt;acronym&gt;' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.acronym","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/acronym/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Das HTML-Element <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/abbr\"><code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<div id=\"sect5\">&nbsp;</div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Attribute","id":"attributes"},{"text":"DOM Schnittstelle","id":"dom_interface"},{"text":"Beispiel","id":"example"},{"text":"Standarddarstellung","id":"default_styling"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Mit dem HTML Acronym Element (<acronym>) können Autoren eine Folge von Zeichen deutlich angeben, aus denen ein Akronym oder eine Abkürzung für ein Wort besteht. Dieses Element wurde in HTML5 entfernt. Verwenden Sie das Element <abbr>.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<acronym>","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"acronym","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<acronym> : l'élément d'acronyme","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<acronym>","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<acronym>","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"<acronym>","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"<acronym>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<acronym>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/html/element/acronym","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/html/element/acronym/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: HyperText Markup Language"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Element"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/acronym","title":"<acronym>"}],"pageTitle":"<acronym> - HTML: HyperText Markup Language | MDN","noIndexing":false}}